"{\"uid\": \"thesouthafrican.com-sport-paris-olympics-2024-novak-djokovic-outclasses-rafael-nadal-at-paris-olympics-2024-result-news\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Copyright Blue Sky Publications (Pty) Ltd. All Rights Reserved.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 63, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 15, \"end\": 18, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Sports\", \"score\": 0.9999775208205421, \"rank\": 2.2422775412777464e-05, \"text\": \"Sky\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Sports\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"thesouthafrican.com is a division of Blue Sky Publications Ltd. Reproduction without permission prohibited  Home\\u00bbSport\\u00bbParis Olympics 2024\\u00bbNovak Djokovic outclasses Rafael Nadal at Paris Olympics 2024  Novak Djokovic defeated Rafael Nadal at the Paris Olympics 2024 on Monday, claiming victory in the pair's 60th and potentially last meeting.\", \"from\": 65, \"to\": 407, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 107, \"end\": 110, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Sports\", \"score\": 0.9999775208205421, \"rank\": 2.2422775412777464e-05, \"text\": \"Sky\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Sports\"}, {\"begin\": 230, \"end\": 242, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rafael Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\"}, {\"begin\": 246, \"end\": 260, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 267, \"end\": 281, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Novak Djokovic\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\"}, {\"begin\": 291, \"end\": 303, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rafael Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Novak DjokovicdefeatedRafael Nadalat the Paris Olympics 2024 on Monday, claiming a6-1, 6-4victory in the pair's60thand potentially last meeting.\", \"from\": 409, \"to\": 553, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Enjoy the Paris Olympic Games 2024 experience at your favourite ATKV Resort!\", \"from\": 555, \"to\": 631, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 619, \"end\": 623, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ATKV\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"ATKV\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ATKV\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ATKV\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was 24-time Grand Slam champion Djokovic's 31st win in a rivalry which began on the same Roland Garros clay courts in 2006.\", \"from\": 633, \"to\": 759, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 668, \"end\": 676, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"score\": 0.9999999995316102, \"rank\": 4.68262486926105e-10, \"text\": \"Djokovic\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\"}, {\"begin\": 725, \"end\": 738, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Open\", \"score\": 0.9999999997307896, \"rank\": 2.6917520956271703e-10, \"text\": \"Roland Garros\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Open\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Open\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nadal was largely outclassed in the much anticipated encounter, only coming briefly to life when he won four games in a row in the second set.\", \"from\": 761, \"to\": 903, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 761, \"end\": 766, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.794120220289958e-15, \"text\": \"Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am very relieved,\\\" said Novak Djokovic.\", \"from\": 905, \"to\": 947, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 932, \"end\": 946, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Novak Djokovic\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Everything was going my way, I was 6-1, 4-0 up but I played a sloppy service game and gave him chances.\\\"\", \"from\": 949, \"to\": 1054, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He added: \\\"I never thought back in 2006 that we'd still be playing each other almost 20 years later.\\\"\", \"from\": 1056, \"to\": 1157, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For the latest Paris Olympics 2024 news, bookmarkThe South African website'sdedicated section for free-to-read content  In a sign of the wear and tear the pair have endured in recent months, Djokovic wore a protective strapping around his right knee while Nadal's right thigh was heavily strapped.\", \"from\": 1159, \"to\": 1456, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1350, \"end\": 1358, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"score\": 0.9999999995316102, \"rank\": 4.68262486926105e-10, \"text\": \"Djokovic\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\"}, {\"begin\": 1415, \"end\": 1420, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.794120220289958e-15, \"text\": \"Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But Djokovic played freely, forcing Nadal to scamper around Court Philippe Chatrier where the Spaniard had collected 14 of his 22 Grand Slam titles.\", \"from\": 1458, \"to\": 1606, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1494, \"end\": 1499, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.794120220289958e-15, \"text\": \"Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\"}, {\"begin\": 1518, \"end\": 1541, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_Roland_Garros\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Court Philippe Chatrier\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_Roland_Garros\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_Roland_Garros\"}, {\"begin\": 1518, \"end\": 1541, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_Roland_Garros\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Court Philippe Chatrier\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_Roland_Garros\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_Roland_Garros\"}, {\"begin\": 1552, \"end\": 1560, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spaniards\", \"score\": 0.8382690543173481, \"rank\": 0.1926162994888387, \"text\": \"Spaniard\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spaniards\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spaniards\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Serb raced to 4-0 lead, on the back of a double break, and held for 5-0 before Nadal stopped the rot much to the relief of a packed, sweltering crowd.\", \"from\": 1608, \"to\": 1762, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1612, \"end\": 1616, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia\", \"score\": 0.8844496502637347, \"rank\": 0.1293762828631314, \"text\": \"Serb\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia\"}, {\"begin\": 1691, \"end\": 1696, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.794120220289958e-15, \"text\": \"Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Djokovic pocketed the one-sided opener when 2008 Olympic gold medallist Nadal ballooned a forehand wide of the mark.\", \"from\": 1764, \"to\": 1880, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1836, \"end\": 1841, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.794120220289958e-15, \"text\": \"Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The statistics made grim reading for the 38-year-old who managed to eke out just four points off the Djokovic serve in the first set.\", \"from\": 1882, \"to\": 2015, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1983, \"end\": 1991, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"score\": 0.9999999995316102, \"rank\": 4.68262486926105e-10, \"text\": \"Djokovic\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There was no respite for Nadal, playing just his seventh tournament of an injury-plagued season, as Djokovic again carved out a double break for a 4-0 lead in the second set.\", \"from\": 2017, \"to\": 2191, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2042, \"end\": 2047, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.794120220289958e-15, \"text\": \"Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\"}, {\"begin\": 2117, \"end\": 2125, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"score\": 0.9999999995316102, \"rank\": 4.68262486926105e-10, \"text\": \"Djokovic\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Djokovic, seeking a first Olympic gold medal to add to his 24 Grand Slam triumphs, surprisingly handed Nadal a lifeline when he served up a double fault to be broken for the first time.\", \"from\": 2193, \"to\": 2378, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2296, \"end\": 2301, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.794120220289958e-15, \"text\": \"Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nadal retrieved the second break to claw his way back from 0-4 to 4-4 as the top seed went suddenly off the boil.\", \"from\": 2380, \"to\": 2493, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Novak Djokovic responded in style, a drop-shot leaving Nadal flat-footed as the Serb broke for 5-4 on a fourth break point and clinched victory in style with an ace.\", \"from\": 2495, \"to\": 2660, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2495, \"end\": 2509, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Novak Djokovic\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\"}, {\"begin\": 2575, \"end\": 2579, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia\", \"score\": 0.8844496502637347, \"rank\": 0.1293762828631314, \"text\": \"Serb\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite his defeat on Monday, Nadal still has hopes of a gold medal in the men's doubles where he is playing alongsideCarlos Alcaraz.\", \"from\": 2662, \"to\": 2795, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2692, \"end\": 2697, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.794120220289958e-15, \"text\": \"Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\"}, {\"begin\": 2787, \"end\": 2794, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.470082431353986e-21, \"text\": \"Alcaraz\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"By Garrin Lambley \\u00a9 Agence France-Presse  WIN R2 000: Take The South African's SASSA Survey  The South African is hiring!\", \"from\": 2797, \"to\": 2918, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2807, \"end\": 2814, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lambley_railway_station\", \"score\": 0.9994020292733972, \"rank\": 0.0005983284493840272, \"text\": \"Lambley\", \"types\":